        "description": {
            "chat": "",
            "unidentified": "",
            "value": "<p>You replicate the fiery venom of the tor linnorm and inflict an enemy with the dread dragon's debilitating bite. You deal [[/r 2d12 #piercing]] piercing damage to the targeted creature and afflict it with tor linnorm venom. If the target takes piercing damage, they must attempt a Fortitude save.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The target is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The target takes [[/r 8d6 #fire]] fire damage.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The target is afflicted with Tor Linnorm Venom at stage 1.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The target is afflicted with tor linnorm venom at stage 2.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Tor Linnorm Venom</strong> (fire, injury, poison) <strong>Level 17</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Maximum Duration</strong> 10 rounds</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 1</strong> [[/r 8d6 #fire]] fire damage and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Drained]{Drained 1} (1 round)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 2</strong> [[/r 12d6 #fire]] fire damage and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Drained]{Drained 2} (1 round)</p>"
